 https://www.imdb.com

test case #1
Summary: Sign in to account

Steps to reproduce:
1. Open https://www.imdb.com
2. Click "Other Sign in options" button. ( opening new page)
3. Click "Sign in with IMDb" button.
4. Input "maksdanish@gmail.com" in field "email".
5. Input "Odyssey100" in field "password".
6. Click "Sign In" button.

Expected result:
User "maksdanish@gmail.com" should be login to private account

test case#2
Summary: Edit Full name in user profile

Pre-condition:
1. Open https://www.imdb.com
2. Click "Other Sign in options" button. ( opening new page)
3. Click "Sign in with IMDb" button.
4. Input "maksdanish@gmail.com" in field "email".
5. Input "Odyssey100" in field "password".
6. Click "Sign In" button.

Steps to reptoduce:
1.Click popup menu with nickname.
2.Click "Account Settings" button
3.Click "Login and security" button.
4.Click  "Edit" button on Name field.
5 Erase data on Full Name field.
6.Input name ,for example: "DanishTest".
7.Click "Submit" button.

Post-condition:
Clear test result and change name back to "maksdanish"

Expected result:
Full Name should be changed.
We should be received msg "You have successfully updated your Name!"

test case#3
Summary: Add a new Watchlist

Pre-condition:
1. Open https://www.imdb.com
2. Click "Other Sign in options" button. ( opening new page)
3. Click "Sign in with IMDb" button.
4. Input "maksdanish@gmail.com" in field "email".
5. Input "Odyssey100" in field "password".
6. Click "Sign In" button.

Steps to reptoduce:
1. Click Watchlist button on main page.
2. Click "Create a new list" button.
3. Input "myVideo" value in "List Title" field.
4. Input "testDesc" value in "List Description" field.
5. Select "peple" in pulldown menu in "type of List".
6. Click "Create" button.
7. Click "Done"button.






